[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_large.png?m=1650127482", "name": "shanghai", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_normal.png?m=1650127482", "title": "上海", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/shanghai", "topics": 3694, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Shanghai", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6f49/22f4/18_mini.png?m=1650127482", "stars": 2454, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 18, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 548096, "username": "juggledf", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/juggledf", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a4938979a4774ab8f4749e8f0b265c20?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a4938979a4774ab8f4749e8f0b265c20?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a4938979a4774ab8f4749e8f0b265c20?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1623395765, "last_modified": 1623395765}, "last_reply_by": "Felix2Yu", "last_touched": 1733154187, "title": "上海房本去名，引发的亲情、利益纠纷", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1094261", "created": 1733106703, "deleted": 0, "content": "背景：我老婆家有套老破小（价值 200 个左右），房产证上是：我老婆她妈和她外婆的名字（外婆已去世、没遗嘱），\r\n打算把她外婆的名字去掉，方便以后售卖。\r\n\r\n房子是我丈母娘自己全款买的（有买房的证明文件）。\r\n\r\n当初加上我老婆外婆名字的原因：是想给老年人晚年一个安全感。\r\n\r\n我老婆有 2 个舅舅，大舅和小舅都知道这个房子是我丈母娘自己买的。\r\n\r\n大舅想通过去名字这个事，找我们要钱，明确说了，他有权益要这部分钱，遗产继承\r\n\r\n小舅不要这个钱，并且全力支持我丈母娘。\r\n\r\n![cop]( https://img.picgo.net/2024/12/02/cop756de4691aa93b4d.png)\r\n我画了简单的关系图\r\n\r\n现在的方案是：\r\n\r\n  1.小舅去和大舅协商，让他放弃这个事，并且协助我们把这个名字去掉\r\n  \r\n  2.如果协商不成功，走民事诉讼\r\n\r\n我和律师咨询下的结果是，大舅可能有权益分享房子六分之一的价值，诉讼有失败的风险\r\n\r\n和公证处咨询，也是需要大舅同意，才能做公证，\r\n\r\n\r\n亲大哥惦记自己妹妹的房子，真特么的恶心。\r\n\r\n发这个帖子想咨询下，有相关经验的人和律师，这件事就一点办法没有吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>背景：我老婆家有套老破小（价值 200 个左右），房产证上是：我老婆她妈和她外婆的名字（外婆已去世、没遗嘱），\n打算把她外婆的名字去掉，方便以后售卖。</p>\n<p>房子是我丈母娘自己全款买的（有买房的证明文件）。</p>\n<p>当初加上我老婆外婆名字的原因：是想给老年人晚年一个安全感。</p>\n<p>我老婆有 2 个舅舅，大舅和小舅都知道这个房子是我丈母娘自己买的。</p>\n<p>大舅想通过去名字这个事，找我们要钱，明确说了，他有权益要这部分钱，遗产继承</p>\n<p>小舅不要这个钱，并且全力支持我丈母娘。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"cop\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://img.picgo.net/2024/12/02/cop756de4691aa93b4d.png\"/>\n我画了简单的关系图</p>\n<p>现在的方案是：</p>\n<p>1.小舅去和大舅协商，让他放弃这个事，并且协助我们把这个名字去掉</p>\n<p>2.如果协商不成功，走民事诉讼</p>\n<p>我和律师咨询下的结果是，大舅可能有权益分享房子六分之一的价值，诉讼有失败的风险</p>\n<p>和公证处咨询，也是需要大舅同意，才能做公证，</p>\n<p>亲大哥惦记自己妹妹的房子，真特么的恶心。</p>\n<p>发这个帖子想咨询下，有相关经验的人和律师，这件事就一点办法没有吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1733106703, "replies": 165, "id": 1094261}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "/static/img/node_default_large.png", "name": "fitness", "avatar_normal": "/static/img/node_default_normal.png", "title": "健身", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/fitness", "topics": 148, "footer": null, "header": null, "title_alternative": "Fitness", "avatar_mini": "/static/img/node_default_mini.png", "stars": 184, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 839, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 393842, "username": "lizhengbo", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lizhengbo", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/29e3/855c/393842_mini.png?m=1705571395", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/29e3/855c/393842_normal.png?m=1705571395", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/29e3/855c/393842_large.png?m=1705571395", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/29e3/855c/393842_xlarge.png?m=1705571395", "created": 1553088437, "last_modified": 1705571395}, "last_reply_by": "ltkun", "last_touched": 1733160968, "title": "每天跑 5~10 万步能减多少？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1094331", "created": 1733116128, "deleted": 0, "content": "辞职了，还有两个月过年，暂时不想回家。\n\n\n\n做了个体检，172cm/95kg....\n\n\n\n之前胖过 185 ，减到 135 ，四五年过去又胖了。\n\n\n\n打算每天跑个几十公里，节食疯狂减肥，两个月不知道能减多少，之前 185→135 花费了四五个月。\n\n\n\n以后出门打工带个体重秤，不然体重不知不觉就上升了。", "content_rendered": "辞职了，还有两个月过年，暂时不想回家。<br /><br /><br /><br />做了个体检，172cm/95kg....<br /><br /><br /><br />之前胖过 185 ，减到 135 ，四五年过去又胖了。<br /><br /><br /><br />打算每天跑个几十公里，节食疯狂减肥，两个月不知道能减多少，之前 185→135 花费了四五个月。<br /><br /><br /><br />以后出门打工带个体重秤，不然体重不知不觉就上升了。", "last_modified": 1733116128, "replies": 155, "id": 1094331}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 27634, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3086, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 564073, "username": "shervy", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/shervy", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fed1/379e/564073_mini.png?m=1733107621", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fed1/379e/564073_normal.png?m=1733107621", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fed1/379e/564073_large.png?m=1733107621", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fed1/379e/564073_xlarge.png?m=1733107621", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fed1/379e/564073_xlarge.png?m=1733107621", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fed1/379e/564073_xlarge.png?m=1733107621", "created": 1638491434, "last_modified": 1733107621}, "last_reply_by": "xin1284", "last_touched": 1733167107, "title": "怎么没有 Mac mini 热了？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1094280", "created": 1733107766, "deleted": 0, "content": "### 买 Mac mini4 变少了吗? ### \r\n\r\n前段时间坛里大部分人都在 **创造需求** ；\r\n\r\n看到别人买自己也想买，不管有没有需要；\r\n\r\n看到补贴完的价格低，自己也想买，强制创造需求；\r\n\r\n这两天 mini4 这类帖子和相关回复好像变少了，\r\n\r\n是因为大家都以创造需求为基础，\r\n\r\n买好了 Mac mini4 放在家里踏上吃灰之路了吗?", "content_rendered": "<h3>买 Mac mini4 变少了吗?</h3>\n<p>前段时间坛里大部分人都在 <strong>创造需求</strong> ；</p>\n<p>看到别人买自己也想买，不管有没有需要；</p>\n<p>看到补贴完的价格低，自己也想买，强制创造需求；</p>\n<p>这两天 mini4 这类帖子和相关回复好像变少了，</p>\n<p>是因为大家都以创造需求为基础，</p>\n<p>买好了 Mac mini4 放在家里踏上吃灰之路了吗?</p>\n", "last_modified": 1733107881, "replies": 144, "id": 1094280}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 6696, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1615, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 140222, "username": "a134698815", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/a134698815", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5878fca1468a42cbbffa9c7aa8819f5f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5878fca1468a42cbbffa9c7aa8819f5f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5878fca1468a42cbbffa9c7aa8819f5f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1443329606, "last_modified": 1733096977}, "last_reply_by": "zhuangqhc", "last_touched": 1733163957, "title": "2024 年 12 月了，一年又见底了，大家都过得怎样呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1094197", "created": 1733096994, "deleted": 0, "content": "去年的帖子： https://www.v2ex.com/t/996699#reply215\r\n\r\n今年更新如下：\r\n\r\n去年 12 月转正成功，老板居然还加薪 5%，不多但还不错。\r\n\r\n3 月正式跟老板提雇主担保的申请，老板同意。\r\n\r\n6 月提交了 186 申请，现在还在等待，目测得等一年。\r\n\r\n7 月老婆正式毕业，结束了两年的 master 生涯，也结束了我两年的供读生活（学费真的好贵啊）。\r\n\r\n9 月老婆找到本地工作，拿到 offer ，开始赚钱。\r\n\r\n11 月定了过年回家的机票，从登陆澳洲之后就没回国过，打算回国待一个月，好好和家人朋友